sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Operator
    participant N as Now pulse
    participant D as Run Drawer
    participant H as useRunStream
    participant A as /api/ge/ledger/runs/:id/events
    participant L as Durable run ledger

    N->>N: poll ledger on a calm cadence
    U->>N: click Now pulse
    N->>D: open Runs, pick a run to Follow
    D->>H: subscribe(runId)
    H->>A: EventSource GET (SSE)
    loop live run
        L->>A: append ledger event
        A-->>H: event (seq, stage, log line)
        H-->>D: reduce into stage timeline + log tail
    end
    A-->>H: stream drop
    H-->>D: show reconnecting indicator
    H->>A: EventSource auto-reconnect
